messages.messageBody:
Just wanted to share,,

If you've been talking about the election process and stuff, Cartoon Network has an election going on and there are some pretty funny political ads that can spur some great conversations.

http://www.cartoonnetwork.com/tv_shows/specials/election/index.html

I love hearing the kids opinions on these things. :)

Kelli~ Wood is Good <g>
